data.description: Experience the ultimate in convenience and comfort with this charming 4-bedroom Cape Cod, perfectly situated in a central location that puts you close to everything. This home is a hidden gem near the airport, Ft Meade, NSA, Naval Academy, DC, and Baltimore, offering the best of both worlds. As you step inside, you'll discover a beautifully renovated interior featuring 4 beds and 2 full baths and a stunning white kitchen with butcher block countertops that make cooking a breeze. The adorable laundry room with ample counter space and storage adds a touch of practicality to daily living. The home boasts updated LVP flooring and fresh paint, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere. Newer windows ensure energy efficiency, and a new water heater provides peace of mind. Step outside to find a spacious and fully fenced yard with a charming custom patio, perfect for outdoor gatherings. The front yard exudes curb appeal, making a memorable first impression. This home is ready to offer you comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own your little oasis!
